## üöÄ User Onboarding

### For New Users

1. Visit https://spliceclips.com
2. Click "Download"
3. Install SPLICE-Installer-6.0.10.pkg
4. Choose CEP or UXP during installation
5. Restart Premiere Pro
6. Activate with license key
7. Start using Quick Edit (now fixed!)

### For Existing Users (Like Danny)

**Option A: Website Download**
1. Download latest from https://spliceclips.com/downloads/SPLICE-Installer-latest.pkg
2. Run installer (overwrites old version)
3. Restart Premiere Pro
4. Quick Edit now works!

**Option B: Direct Hotfix**
1. Use previously sent SPLICE-CEP-v6.0.10-HOTFIX-Danny.zip
2. Follow installation guide
3. Same result as Option A

